        "body": { "en": "Set the right block the same 2 mm clear of the frame-corner plate as the left block — keep both gaps equal so the idler stations stay symmetric.", "zh": "右边的支座和左边一样，离框架转角连接板留 2 mm 间隙——两边间隙相等，惰轮工位才能左右对称。" },
